Check If Health Monitoring is turned on. Health Monitoring is turned on by default in the machine level Web.Config file:
      <healthMonitoring heartbeatInterval="0" enabled="true">  <bufferModes/>  <providers/>  <profiles/>  <rules/>  <eventMappings/></healthMonitoring>
      If the Enabled attribute is set to false in your machine or application level config file, then health monitoring has been turned off.&nbsp;
